data.description: BASEMENT, HARDWOODS, METAL ROOF and HUGE LOT LOCATION... A spacious 1.2-acre lot in the heart of Dawsonville, GA. This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath property offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life, while still being conveniently located near US 19 for easy access to all amenities and attractions.  Included is an unfinished basement for storage, workshop or hobby space.
